  "text": "Borreliosis also leads to lymphocytic infiltration of epineurial blood vessel walls associated with perineurial thickening and fibrosis and axonal neuropathy. A characteristic pattern of perineurial TNF-α, C5b-9, and ICAM-1 expression has been found in sural nerve biopsies of borreliosis patients [CITATION_1] .",
